    &gt;ElastiFlow™&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/robcowart/elastiflow/issues/428&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Problem with elasticsearch-oss #428&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/robcowart/elastiflow/blob/master/DOCKER.md#prepare-the-data-path&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Running ElastiFlow™ on Docker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
